dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and spot heights. Map shows: International boundaries, 1949 Armistice Line, demilitarized zone limit, Israeli-developed area (civilian) beyond the 1949 Armistice Line, abandoned/dismantled Syrian villages, antiquity sites, mines and quarries, and four classes of roads. Shipping list no.: 92-0343-P. "Depictions of roads outside of the Golan Heights are current as of September 1983." "802028 (R00418) 4-92."
